le\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-cyan\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Spetum.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Spetum.png\" src=\"/images/4/4f/Spetum.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>大战戟\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td>长柄叉\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（小型）\n</th>\n<td>d6+1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>伤害（大型）\n</th>\n<td>2d6\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>命中修正\n</th>\n<td>+0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>武器技能类别\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>规格\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8F%8C%E6%89%8B&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"双手 (page does not exist)\">双手</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>5 <a href=\"/wiki/Zm/zh-CN\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Zm/zh-CN\">zm</a><br />（+10/正数附魔等级）\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">50</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>材料\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>大战戟</b>（spetum）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"武器\">武器</a>，它是一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器</a>，由<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"铁 (page does not exist)\">铁</a>制成，未<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%89%B4%E5%AE%9A&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"鉴定 (page does not exist)\">鉴定</a>时外观为<b>长柄叉</b>（forked polearm）。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">起源</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#GruntHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">GruntHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#xNetHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">xNetHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#EvilHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">EvilHack</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#SlashTHEM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SlashTHEM</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">百科文本</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%AD%A6%E5%8D%AB%E5%91%98&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"警卫员 (page does not exist)\">警卫员</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%A3%AB%E5%85%B5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"士兵 (page does not exist)\">士兵</a>在生成时有概率<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"怪物起始物品 (page does not exist)\">获得</a>一把大战戟<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B7%A8%E9%AD%94%EF%BC%88%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E7%B1%BB%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%89&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"巨魔（怪物类别） (page does not exist)\">巨魔</a>类怪物生成时有<sup>1</sup>&#8260;<sub>8</sub>的概率携带一把大战戟<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>大战戟的重量是所有长柄武器中最轻的（50 <a href=\"/index.php?title=Aum/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Aum/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">aum</a>），它的伤害输出能力也不错，对大型怪物的伤害与<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%96%A7%E6%9E%AA\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"斧枪\">斧枪</a>在长柄武器中并列第二。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>大战戟最初于<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_1.3d\" title=\"NetHack 1.3d\">NetHack 1.3d</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"起源\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\">起源</span></h2>\n<div class=\"noprint sidebox\">\n<div style=\"float: left;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"维基百科\"><img alt=\"维基百科\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png/50px-Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 60px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:Main_Page\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:Main Page\">维基百科</a>相关条目：\n<div style=\"margin-left: 10px;\"><i><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Search/Spetum\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Special:Search/Spetum\">Spetum </a></b></i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:152px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Spetums.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/30/Spetums.png/150px-Spetums.png\" width=\"150\" height=\"78\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/30/Spetums.png/225px-Spetums.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/30/Spetums.png/300px-Spetums.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Spetums.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>大战戟</div></div></div>\n<p>大战戟是13世纪在欧洲出现的一种长柄武器。它的柄一般有1.8&#xff5e;2.4米长，其矛头一般有30&#xff5e;36厘米长，基部的两侧各有一个单侧开刃的“分叉”，长度一般是矛头的一半，与矛头形成锐角。NetHack对大战戟外观的描述“长柄叉”其实不太准确：这个词其实更适合描述由农用干草叉改制的<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_fork\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Military fork\">军用叉</a>类武器，参见<a href=\"/wiki/File:Forks.jpg\" title=\"File:Forks.jpg\">此图片</a>。\n</p><p>根据古物研究者约翰·休伊特（John Hewitt）的看法，大战戟被认为是<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%98%94%E5%A4%B4%E6%9E%AA\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"阔头枪\">阔头枪</a>的一种变种，它与阔头枪和<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%8B%E9%92%AF\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"镋钯\">镋钯</a>的主要区别在于枪头上用于斩击的刃。这些刃可以牵制敌人及缴械，其刀背则可以击落敌人的盾牌。\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Spetum/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"GruntHack\">GruntHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/GruntHack\" title=\"GruntHack\">GruntHack</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Vlad_the_Impaler\" title=\"Vlad the Impaler\">Vlad the Impaler</a> is always generated with a <a href=\"/wiki/Object_properties#GruntHack\" title=\"Object properties\">thirsty</a> spetum.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"xNetHack\">xNetHack</span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/XNetHack\" title=\"XNetHack\">xNetHack</a> removes the spetum and many other polearms.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/EvilHack\" title=\"EvilHack\">EvilHack</a>, a spetum can be created at a <a href=\"/wiki/Forge_(dungeon_feature)\" title=\"Forge (dungeon feature)\">forge</a> by combining a <a href=\"/wiki/Knife\" title=\"Knife\">knife</a> and a <a href=\"/wiki/Spear\" title=\"Spear\">spear</a>. This also applies to <a href=\"/wiki/Hack%27EM\" title=\"Hack&#39;EM\">Hack'EM</a>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SlashTHEM\" title=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Troll_(starting_race)\" title=\"Troll (starting race)\">troll</a> characters that are not <a href=\"/wiki/Convict\" title=\"Convict\">Convicts</a> have a <sup>1</sup>&#8260;<sub>4</sub> chance of generating with a spetum as their starting polearm.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"百科文本\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\">百科文本</span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>请参阅<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%95%BF%E6%9F%84%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8#.E7.99.BE.E7.A7.91.E6.96.87.E6.9C.AC\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"长柄武器\">长柄武器的百科文本</a>。</i></dd></dl>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L194\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 194</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L451\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 451</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926190630\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.040 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.061 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 529/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2646/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5234/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 777/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 827/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   43.477      1 -total\n 31.90%   13.869      1 Template:Languages\n 27.50%   11.958      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 13.58%    5.903      2 Template:Refsrc\n 11.10%    4.824      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 10.01%    4.354      1 Template:Weapon/zh-CN\n  8.23%    3.576      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n  8.02%    3.489      1 Template:Translation/zh-CN\n  6.73%    2.924      2 Template:Frac\n  5.80%    2.521      2 Template:Refsrc/link\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:39520-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926190630 and revision id 166835\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Spetum/zh-CN&amp;oldi