l pages</a></li><li id=\"t-print\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spetum/zh-CN&amp;printable=yes\" rel=\"alternate\" title=\"Printable version of this page [p]\" accesskey=\"p\">Printable version</a></li><li id=\"t-permalink\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spetum/zh-CN&amp;oldid=166835\" title=\"Permanent link to this revision of the page\">Permanent link</a></li><li id=\"t-info\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Spetum/zh-CN&amp;action=info\" title=\"More information about this page\">Page information</a></li>\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"footer\" role=\"contentinfo\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"footer-info\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"footer-info-lastmod\"> This page was last edited on 18 April 2024, at 11:43.</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"footer-places\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"footer-places-about\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:About\" title=\"NetHackWiki:About\">About NetHackWiki</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"footer-places-disclaimer\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:General_disclaimer\" title=\"NetHackWiki:General disclaimer\">Disclaimers</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul id=\"footer-icons\" class=\"noprint\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"footer-poweredbyico\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"//www.mediawiki.org/\"><img src=\"/resources/assets/poweredby_mediawiki_88x31.png\" alt=\"Powered by MediaWiki\" srcset=\"/resources/assets/poweredby_mediawiki_132x47.png 1.5x, /resources/assets/poweredby_mediawiki_176x62.png 2x\" width=\"88\" height=\"31\"/></a>\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgPageParseReport\":{\"limitreport\":{\"cputime\":\"0.040\",\"walltime\":\"0.061\",\"ppvisitednodes\":{\"value\":529,\"limit\":1000000},\"ppgeneratednodes\":{\"value\":2646,\"limit\":1000000},\"postexpandincludesize\":{\"value\":5234,\"limit\":2097152},\"templateargumentsize\":{\"value\":777,\"limit\":2097152},\"expansiondepth\":{\"value\":9,\"limit\":40},\"expensivefunctioncount\":{\"value\":4,\"limit\":100},\"unstrip-depth\":{\"value\":0,\"limit\":20},\"unstrip-size\":{\"value\":827,\"limit\":5000000},\"timingprofile\":[\"100.00%   43.477      1 -total\",\" 31.90%   13.869      1 Template:Languages\",\" 27.50%   11.958      5 Template:Languages/Lang\",\" 13.58%    5.903      2 Template:Refsrc\",\" 11.10%    4.824      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\",\" 10.01%    4.354      1 Template:Weapon/zh-CN\",\"  8.23%    3.576      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\",\"  8.02%    3.489      1 Template:Translation/zh-CN\",\"  6.73%    2.924      2 Template:Frac\",\"  5.80%    2.521      2 Template:Refsrc/link\"]},\"cachereport\":{\"timestamp\":\"20240926190630\",\"ttl\":604800,\"transientcontent\":false}}});mw.config.set({\"wgBackendResponseTime\":95});});</script>\n\t</body>\n</html>\n","rawPage":"{{needhelp/zh-CN}}\n{{languages}}\n{{weapon/zh-CN\n |name=大战戟\n |tile=[[image:spetum.png]]\n |appearance=长柄叉\n |smalldmg=d6+1\n |largedmg=2d6\n |tohit=<nowiki>+0</nowiki>\n |skill=长柄武器\n |size=双手\n |cost=5\n |weight=50\n |material=铁\n}}\n'''大战戟'''（spetum）是{{cnlink|NetHack}}中的一种[[武器]]，它是一种[[长柄武器]]，由[[铁]]制成，未[[鉴定]]时外观为'''长柄叉'''（forked polearm）。\n\n== 生成 ==\n[[警卫员]]和[[士兵]]在生成时有概率[[怪物起始物品|获得]]一把大战戟{{refsrc|src/makemon.c|194|version=NetHack 3.6.7}}。[[巨魔（怪物类别）|巨魔]]类怪物生成时有{{frac|8}}的概率携带一把大战戟{{refsrc|src/makemon.c|451|version=NetHack 3.6.7}}。\n\n== 策略 ==\n大战戟的重量是所有长柄武器中最轻的（50 {{cnlink|aum}}），它的伤害输出能力也不错，对大型怪物的伤害与[[斧枪]]在长柄武器中并列第二。\n\n== 历史 ==\n大战戟最初于[[NetHack 1.3d]]加入游戏。\n\n== 起源 ==\n{{wikipedia/zh-CN}}\n[[Image:Spetums.png|150px|thumb|right|大战戟]]\n大战戟是13世纪在欧洲出现的一种长柄武器。它的柄一般有1.8{{波浪线}}2.4米长，其矛头一般有30{{波浪线}}36厘米长，基部的两侧各有一个单侧开刃的“分叉”，长度一般是矛头的一半，与矛头形成锐角。NetHack对大战戟外观的描述“长柄叉”其实不太准确：这个词其实更适合描述由农用干草叉改制的[[Wikipedia:Military fork|军用叉]]类武器，参见[[:File:Forks.jpg|此图片]]。\n\n根据古物研究者约翰·休伊特（John Hewitt）的看法，大战戟被认为是[[阔头枪]]的一种变种，它与阔头枪和[[镋钯]]的主要区别在于枪头上用于斩击的刃。这些刃可以牵制敌人及缴械，其刀背则可以击落敌人的盾牌。\n\n==Variants==\n{{translation/zh-CN|n}}\n===GruntHack===\nIn [[GruntHack]], [[Vlad the Impaler]] is always generated with a [[Object properties#GruntHack|thirsty]] spetum.\n\n===xNetHack===\n[[xNetHack]] removes the spetum and many other polearms.\n\n===EvilHack===\nIn [[EvilHack]], a spetum can be created at a [[Forge (dungeon feature)|forge]] by combining a [[knife]] and a [[spear]]. This also applies to [[Hack'EM]].\n\n===SlashTHEM===\nIn [[SlashTHEM]], [[Troll (starting race)|troll]] characters that are not [[Convict]]s have a {{frac|4}} chance of generating with a spetum as their starting polearm.\n\n== 百科文本 ==\n{{encyclopedia-redirect/zh-CN|长柄武器}}\n\n== 引用及注释 ==\n<references/>\n{{nethack-367/zh-CN}}\n[[Category:Weapons/zh-CN|DAZHANJI]]"}